&lt;h1 id="the-top-idea-in-your-mind"&gt;The Top Idea in Your Mind&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;July 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I realized recently that what one thinks about in the shower in the morning is more important than I&amp;rsquo;d thought. I knew it was a good time to have ideas. Now I&amp;rsquo;d go further: now I&amp;rsquo;d say it&amp;rsquo;s hard to do a really good job on anything you don&amp;rsquo;t think about in the shower.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>